Testing personal protective equipment (PPE) inventory Deloitte
New

Testing personal protective equipment (PPE) inventory, burn rates, and demand forecasts. The data included contains: the inventory of PPE stock in each testing location, the utilisation rate of PPE at each location, forecast demand and opening and closing stock projections for each day. This data is used to support the PPE dashboard


Testing site predicted capacity Deloitte
New

This dataset includes details of the predicted capacity of all testing sites at specific dates, based on inventory of the number of testing kits available and predicted demand.


Testing site predicted demand Deloitte
New

This dataset includes details about the predicted demand for testing at each site.
